{"tid":905234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前AV女優回鍋 拍無碼片放國外賣","createTime":"2018-11-17T03:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:19:45.000Z","uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f716e1b685738253ed52c64ca8e1d73d7365842f","tid":905234,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本AV產業蓬勃，其中也有業者從事非法拍攝的行為，近日就有AV製作公司的社長，夥同前AV女優製作無碼性愛片，並於國外網站販售營利，因此遭到警方逮捕，警方表示不法獲利的銷售額約有6300萬日圓（約1700萬新台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8evi0V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8evi0V.png&h=52677a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《日視NEWS24》<br />\n<br />\n據日媒《日視NEWS24》報導，日本警方最近逮捕了49歲的AV影片製作公司社長須田雅人、以及36歲的前AV女優土屋亞沙美，警方指出，兩人涉嫌於7月製作無碼成人影片，並在國外的付費影片網站上銷售，警方至少找到了50支無碼A片。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuYcxkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuYcxkX.png&h=313bb74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《日視NEWS24》<br />\n<br />\n然而對於警方的調查，須田雅人、土屋亞沙美兩人皆保持緘默，就有網友推測前AV女優土屋亞沙美應是使用了本名，而目前尚未確認其藝名、作品，但從新聞畫面中警方公布的證物中，一旁的浴衣跟羽川流菜(羽川るな)拍片時穿的相似，也引發外界聯想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTpZWNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTpZWNE.png&h=a9e75787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《日視NEWS24》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsurBNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsurBNG.png&h=13a0417b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自caribbean"},{"pid":"d7024d842fa17e4642039a7fbc8dffd06819a32e","tid":905234,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"係 片呢？"},{"pid":"69c69c413900ddd29bb6a613ff89640c1b83ea7f","tid":905234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d7024d842fa17e4642039a7fbc8dffd06819a32e","tid":905234,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"係 片呢